      "title": "80 minutes power cut tomorrow and the day after",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Public Utilities Commission has authorized the Ceylon Electricity Board to cut power tomorrow (15) and tomorrow (16) for an hour and 20 minutes.",
        "Thus for categories A,B,C,D,E,F,G,H,I,J,K,L,P,Q,R,S,T,U,V,W from 5 PM to 9 PM. The electricity cut will be done during that time."
      ],
